import { Flex, Box, Text, Center } from '@chakra-ui/react'

const heading = {
  fontSize: 48,
  fontWeight: 700,
  textAlign: 'left' as const,
  letterSpacing: '2px',
  color: 'space_cadet',
  pl: '1%',
  verticalAlign: 'center' as const
}

const center = {
  fontSize: 24,
  fontWeight: 200,
  textAlign: 'center' as const,
  color: 'ultra_violet',
  w: '33%',
  verticalAlign: 'center' as const
}

export default function Heading() {
  return (
    <Flex align={'center'}>
      <Box w='50%' h='100%'>
        <Text {...heading} >Ari Wisenburn</Text>
      </Box>
      <Box flex='1' h='73px' verticalAlign='center'>
        <Flex flexBasis={'end'}>
          <Center {...center}>
            Projects
          </Center>
          <Center {...center}>
            Contact
          </Center>
          <Center {...center}>
            Download Resume
          </Center>
        </Flex>
      </Box>
    </Flex >
  )
}
